      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay cool, sounds like a plan. i'll try those drops tonight. honestly though, i've heard that if you use too much peroxide it can actually hurt your eardrum if it's already irritated from the qtip. is there like a safe amount i should use so i don't make it worse? and can i just use regular warm water if i run out of drops?",
